scene.message:
Ayase: Ah!{nl}
You okay?!{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Quit spacing out!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Ah!{nl}
Are you okay?!{nl}
Hold it right there, demon!{waitkey}{ret}

Demon: Heh, here they come.{nl}
Tonight my fists hunger{nl}
for blood.{nl}
Let the blood-flowers bloom!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, you!{nl}
It's dangerous! Get back!{nl}
{wait_fr:88}...Y-you're...{nl}
You're Kido?!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: You lot...?{nl}
Stay back...{nl}
This one's mine to kill.{waitkey}{ret}

Demon: Hoh, a spirited brat.{nl}
For that nerve, I'll{nl}
feast on you first.{waitkey}{nl}
Rue your weakness in hell.{waitkey}{ret}
